description: Demolition of the five existing 2 and 3 storey residential blocks and redevelopment of the site to provide a new single block of between 7 storeys and 13 storeys containing 116 homes comprising: 42 x 1 bed; 49 x 2 bed; 24 x 3 bed; 1 x 4 bed units, together with associated cycle parking, car parking, highways, and landscaping.
